{
  "texts": [
    "Note that we implemented an instructional manipulation check (IMC), a popular technique to identify inattentive crowd workers, to ensure the integrity of our data collection process.",
    "Furthermore, we rejected crowd workers using mobile/tablet devices so that all participants could perform tasks on the same layout on their PCs.",
    "Participants were randomly allocated into one of the above four UIs.",
    "They then conducted tasks to summarize their opinions about three randomly allocated themes.",
    "To consider individual differences, we measured and analyzed personal factors as covariates, including the frequency of using chatbots for information seeking, interest in task themes, and familiarity with the themes."
  ]
}